Company Overview of Redwood Capital Investments, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Redwood Capital Investments, LLC is a private equity firm specializing in turnaround, mature and cash flow–generating companies. For special opportunities, the firm invests in credit investments, rescue capital, real estate, distressed debt, fund investments, structured equity securities, and minority equity investments. Within private equity, the firm prefers to invest in basic materials, consumer staples, energy, healthcare, industrials, infrastructure, and railway. It seeks to invest in companies based in the North America region with domestic or global operations, Africa, Asia, Europe, and Latin America and Caribbean. The firm seeks to invest between $10 million and $100 million in compa...
Redwood Capital Investments, LLC is a private equity firm specializing in turnaround, mature and cash flow–generating companies. For special opportunities, the firm invests in credit investments, rescue capital, real estate, distressed debt, fund investments, structured equity securities, and minority equity investments. Within private equity, the firm prefers to invest in basic materials, consumer staples, energy, healthcare, industrials, infrastructure, and railway. It seeks to invest in companies based in the North America region with domestic or global operations, Africa, Asia, Europe, and Latin America and Caribbean. The firm seeks to invest between $10 million and $100 million in companies with a minimum enterprise value between $50 million and $250 million. For special opportunities, the firm can invest in various stages globally. The firm can also occasionally co-invest with other investment firms. Redwood Capital Investments, LLC was founded in 2006 and is based in Baltimore, Maryland.
Detailed Description


