About: Redwood Capital Investments














About
Professionals
Portfolio
Contact








Redwood is a private investment firm. We have a permanent capital base, a creative approach to investing, and the ability to be agile in our decision-making. We partner with strong management teams to build long-term value in exceptional companies.

Overview
Redwood Capital Investments, LLC manages the capital of a small group of private investors in Baltimore, Maryland. Our investors founded and created the largest privately-held staffing company in the United States and therefore understand what it takes to build successful companies — great management teams who have a passion for business.

Strategy
Redwood’s primary objective is to be a long-term partner with strong management teams and family business owners to build businesses that create value. We seek to diversify our portfolio through investments in special opportunities, real estate, and funds with select portfolio managers.
Redwood does not have any required return thresholds. Rather, we evaluate each investment individually, focusing on value creation and the generation of superior risk-adjusted returns. Due to the permanent capital base provided by our investors, we have a long-term investment horizon. Because our team is small and our investors are accessible, we are agile in our decision-making. This enables us to provide creative solutions that can be tailored to individual investment needs.
We take a fair and straightforward approach, seeking to partner with management teams who have an ownership mentality.



Copyright Redwood Capital Investments, LLC
Legal | Privacy










Redwood Capital Investments














Professionals
Portfolio
Contact










Overview
Redwood Capital Investments, LLC is the private investment company for the founders of Allegis Group, the largest privately-held staffing company in the United States. Our primary objective is to invest with founders and management teams in privately held businesses.  Our permanent capital base allows us to offer a unique partnership. We do not underwrite investments with an eye toward the exit. Instead, we focus on creating value through compounded earnings growth over long time horizons. We have a small team, make quick decisions, and develop creative investment structures throughout the equity capital structure to suit the particular needs of companies and business owners.
We look for businesses with the following characteristics:


Understandable, durable business model with a proven earnings track record
Strong position in a niche market with sustainable competitive advantages
Established in-place management team
Opportunities to reinvest earnings or deploy additional capital into the business


In addition to our investments in private businesses, we invest in real estate, infrastructure and marketable securities on an opportunistic basis.





Copyright Redwood Capital Investments, LLC
Redwood Capital Investments, LLC does not provide investment advisory services and does not solicit or permit new investors.
Legal | Privacy










